title: HP MSA 2040: Volume Health Status
agents: linux
catalog: hw/storagehw/hp
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check reports the number of volumes and the health states of all volumes
 of a HP MSA 2040 storage system.

 If the states of all volumes are "OK" then the service state is OK.
 Otherwise the service shows the health status and reason of the volumes
 which are not "OK" and changes to WARN or CRIT.

inventory:
 One service is created.
